faq_rewards_distribution_a:
They are distributed among contributors proportionally to votes received and locked balances.

Every day, {dailyLockedPct}% of the total locked balance is added to locked balances, and {dailyLiquidPct}% is distributed as liquid {symbol}.

Both kinds of emission are split {byVotesPct}/{byVotesAndBalancePct}:{#ul}{#li}{byVotesPct}% goes proportionally to votes received. It benefits primarily work contributors, no matter how much they have locked.{/li}{#li}The other {byVotesAndBalancePct}% goes proportionally to votes multiplied by locked balance. It benefits primarily financial contributors.{/li}{/ul}
